{
  "id": "69c8ee647e5b26dee7ca24fe",
  "title": "語録",
  "created": 1774775920,
  "updated": 1774792311,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69c8ee647e5b26dee7ca24fe",
      "text": "語録",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774775920,
      "updated": 1774775920
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ee6f0000000000c721dc",
      "text": " 誰かが語った言葉を収集したもの",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774775920,
      "updated": 1774775929
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ef7e0000000000c721ee",
      "text": " また、そこに所属してる言葉を指すときに使う?",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774776190,
      "updated": 1774776348
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8efc60000000000c721f0",
      "text": " 格言集みたいなもの",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774776262,
      "updated": 1774776428
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8f05e0000000000c721f2",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774776414,
      "updated": 1774776414
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ee840000000000c721e2",
      "text": "語録の例",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774775940,
      "updated": 1774775942
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ee850000000000c721e3",
      "text": " [喜嶋語録]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774775942,
      "updated": 1774776001
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8eec10000000000c721e6",
      "text": "  大学教授の[喜嶋先生]が研究室で学生に言った名言?を集めたもの",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774776001,
      "updated": 1774776052
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ef3f0000000000c721eb",
      "text": "  [喜嶋先生の静かな世界]という小説に登場する",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774776127,
      "updated": 1774776136
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8eef70000000000c721e8",
      "text": "  先生の言った強い言葉を集めて、学生同士で会話中に用いるとかする",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774776055,
      "updated": 1774776122
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ee8d0000000000c721e4",
      "text": " [淫夢語録]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774775949,
      "updated": 1774776004
    },
    {
      "id": "69c8ef670000000000c721ed",
      "text": "  [真夏の夜の淫夢]などのゲイポルノビデオのセリフを集めたもの",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774776167,
      "updated": 1774776169
    },
    {
      "id": "69c92dc70000000000b63c54",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774792135,
      "updated": 1774792135
    },
    {
      "id": "69c92dc70000000000b63c55",
      "text": "淫夢語録が淫夢語ではなく、忍殺語は忍殺語録ではない",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774792135,
      "updated": 1774792210
    },
    {
      "id": "69c92dee0000000000b63c57",
      "text": " なんで？[vlzs.icon]",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774792175,
      "updated": 1774792190
    },
    {
      "id": "69c92dcb0000000000b63c56",
      "text": " 自分が見たことがないだけで存在する？",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774792140,
      "updated": 1774792224
    },
    {
      "id": "69c92e210000000000b63c59",
      "text": " 〇〇語には言語のイメージを感じる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774792226,
      "updated": 1774792305
    },
    {
      "id": "69c92e390000000000b63c5a",
      "text": "  英語やイタリア語と同列に並ぶ感じ",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774792250,
      "updated": 1774792270
    },
    {
      "id": "69c92e500000000000b63c5b",
      "text": " 語録には格言集のニュアンスを感じる",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774792272,
      "updated": 1774792311
    },
    {
      "id": "69c92e130000000000b63c58",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "63042e42f2ab90001d68385a",
      "created": 1774792212,
      "updated": 1774792212
    }
  ]
}